            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "+ + + A simple WW2 zombie shooter game. \nBase game on sale worth its price in case you like zombie games and you want to play it with friends. The WW2 atmosphere is a nice extra for it. You get quite a few enemy tipes and fine missions. \n\n- - - The game is FULL OF WITH PAYWALLS. \nApart from 3 starting weapons all the rest are unlockable via microtransactions only. What??? \nOh and not only weapons. Most maps, missions, and skins are locked behind paywalls. Around 80% of the game....\nHard NO for this greed. \n- - - The in game music is terrible."
        },
